data.description: GORGEOUS, 1 OWNER HOME HOME WITH POPULAR BONAIRE ADDRESS, COUNTY TAXES ONLY, PREMIER SCHOOL ZONES & GAMEDAY BACK PORCH! This Fabulous 2 Story Home is Well Maintained & features Easy Maintenance Brick Front & Vinyl Siding Exterior with Nice Front Porch. The Interior boasts of Beautiful Engineered Hardwood Flooring throughout the Grand Foyer with Wood Staircase & Gorgeous Metal Railing, Elegant Formal Dining Room with Prairie Style Coffered Ceiling & Decorative Judges Panels, Gorgeous Kitchen with Beautiful Cabinetry, Granite Countertops, OVERSIZED PANTRY & All Stainless Steel Appliances Remain to Include the Refrigerator. POPULAR OPEN FLOOR PLAN with Kitchen Open to Breakfast Area & Large Great Room featuring Electric Fireplace. All Bedrooms are Located on the Second Level and features a HUGE PRIMARY BEDROOM & Spacious Primary Bath offering Dual Vanity, Garden Tub, Custom Tile Shower, & MASSIVE DOUBLE WALK IN CLOSETS. Your Family & Guests will Appreciate the Spacious Guest Bedrooms with Nice Closets & Access to Full Guest Bath.  Enjoy Relaxing or Entertaining on the Beautiful "Game Day" Back Porch with Wood Burning Fireplace featuring Floor To Ceiling Brick Surround & Hearth & TV Hook Ups overlooking the Spacious Backyard with Privacy Fence. Other Features Include 1/2 Bath on the Main Level for Guests and Custom Built In Lockers off the Garage for Additional Storage, Spacious Laundry Room with WASHER & DRYER REMAINING Conveniently Located on the Second Level near all the Bedrooms, Beautiful Tile Flooring in the Baths & Laundry Room, CARPET ONLY IN BEDROOMS & UPSTAIRS LANDING, 2"Blinds, Gutters, Sprinkler System, 2 Car Garage & More! Some Photos Have Been Virtually Staged.
